query: SELECT u.id, u.name, ep.eventId, ep.status, ep.reflexao, sw.title as webinar_title FROM users u LEFT JOIN event_participation ep ON u.id = ep.alunoId LEFT JOIN scheduled_webinars sw ON ep.eventId = sw.id WHERE u.name LIKE '%Valci%' LIMIT 20
